verbose_text: Strikingly, while being absent or weakly expressed in all TC (10) (XREF_FIG A, 6B, and 6M) and in all AC (6) samples (XREF_FIG D, 6E, and 6M), NFIB was highly expressed in 22 out of 26 SCLC samples, including those derived from primary (13 out of 15) and metastatic (9 out of 11) sites (XREF_FIG J, 6K, and 6M).
